text: Farcimen is a genus of land snails with an operculum, terrestrial gastropod mollusks in the family Megalomastomatidae. == Species == Species within the genus Farcimen include: * Farcimen alutaceum (Menke in Pfeiffer, 1846)"Mollusca" .
